---
import NoteLayout from '../../layouts/NoteLayout.astro';
---

<NoteLayout 
  title="Sample Note" 
  date={new Date('2024-01-15')}
  tags={['example', 'demo']}
>
  <p>This is a sample note demonstrating the note layout with TOC on the right.</p>

  <h2>Introduction</h2>
  <p>Notes are single-page articles with a table of contents on the right side.</p>

  <h2>Features</h2>
  <p>The note layout includes:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Automatic table of contents generation</li>
    <li>Share buttons for social media</li>
    <li>Responsive design</li>
    <li>Clean typography</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Subsection Example</h3>
  <p>This is a subsection that will appear indented in the TOC.</p>

  <h2>Conclusion</h2>
  <p>This layout is perfect for quick reference articles and one-pagers.</p>
</NoteLayout>
